<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Say it Again – Support</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1e2f, #3a3a6a);
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 40px;
            color: #ffd166;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #ffd166;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Say it Again</h1>
    <p><strong>Support</strong></p>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>About the App</h2>
        <p>
            Say it Again is an educational party game based on recognizing quotes from movies,
            TV shows, and other pop culture content. The app works with physical cards and
            also allows fully online gameplay.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
            If you have any issues or questions, feel free to contact:
        </p>
        <p>
            📧 Email: <a href="mailto:your@email.com">your@email.com</a>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>FAQ</h2>
        <p><strong>The app has no sound:</strong><br>
        Please check your volume settings and internet connection.</p>

        <p><strong>QR code is not working:</strong><br>
        Make sure you scan the code in good lighting and your camera is focused.</p>

        <p><strong>Online mode is not working:</strong><br>
        Try restarting the app or checking your network connection.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>Privacy</h2>
        <p>
            The Say it Again app does not collect personal data without the user's knowledge.
        </p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        © 2026 Say it Again. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>
